fulltitle: Mr. Handy's Blues: A Musical Documentary
description:
Documentary Film from FishNet Films.
This is a documentary in progress about the Father of the Blues.  To learn more about the film, which is 80% complete, please visit our non-profit fiscal sponsor site Cinema South: www.cinemasouth.org  All contributions to the production of the film are 100% tax deductible.  Thank you!  We want to finish the film by the end of 2014 to celebrate the 100th anniversary of "St. Louis Blues", W.C. Handy's most iconic composition.
title: Mr. Handy's Blues: A Musical Documentary
